author: Heidi Williams | The Oregonian/OregonLive
title: My Dog's Face Round 2: Large Dog vote-offs
text:
Congratulations, remaining canines! You made it to Round 2, proving that you do indeed have a distinguished face.
Now things get even more interesting: Below are all of your fellow Large Dog Round 2 vote-offs. You have two days to get your vote in.
See Small Dog Round 2 vote-offs here.
On Monday, we'll post Round 2 results and start vote-offs for our Final 16, then the Elite Eight and, finally, Four. Check back at oregonlive.com/pets for voting updates.
One winner will be chosen for each category. And yes, there is a prize! Each top dog gets a custom portrait in acrylic of his or her beautiful canine face (painted and donated by Portland artist Minae Lee ) and a $100 gift certificate to the pet store of choice. Winning entries may be published in The Oregonian or on OregonLive.
See official contest rules here .
See all Round 1 winners here .
